msg: TIKA-747: Ogg Vorbis and FLAC Parsers
Use the shade plugin instead of the bundle plugin to merge all dependencies into the single tika-app jar.
This way we can leverage shade's services resource transformer to merge the META-INF/services/ files from all upstream jars.
